metadata.name: I Am She: Lady of the Lake
metadata.description:
A whimsical sunrise sets the backdrop for the Lady of the Lake. She is the calm in the midst of life and the buzz of nature. She is the peace in the storm of the world around her. She is tranquil mornings ushering in fresh hope. She is a perpetual bloom of transformation. I am she, and she is me.

2448 x 3264 px
